{"code": 0, "data": [{"cid": 1105261, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不大", "timestamp": 1613551327, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105262, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Alice", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "放心选", "timestamp": 1613551340, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105266, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "听闻要写各种东西，具体有哪些吖", "timestamp": 1613551364, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105268, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "党课easy", "timestamp": 1613551397, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105273, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Carol", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "不大不大，一个亿嘛", "timestamp": 1613551430, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105280, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Bob", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "党课应该是最水的课之一了，pre、思想汇报和考试也比较简单。pre做得最好的小组还可以到新清华学堂做pre（清华普通的课可没有这个机会，而且不缺观众）。\n总体而言，党课还是一个看态度的课，可以很划水也可以很卷。如果已经提交入党申请书，可以和联系人多聊天，一定要记得及时写思想汇报。", "timestamp": 1613551615, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105401, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Dave", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "思想汇报（如果要入党的话反正也要写的）\n一次出校的参观以及相关的感想写作（我去的是北大红楼，也有国博什么的）\n一个期末的pre（各院系支部自己组织，要求视院系不同而定）\n期末闭卷考试（还好，记pf，除非态度极其不端正不然都能过）", "timestamp": 1613553545, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105596, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Eve", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "接近于0", "timestamp": 1613556458, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1105908, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Francis", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "cz上学期选的 除了有个小组pre和期末考以外什么都没有", "timestamp": 1613560151, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1106759, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": true, "name": "洞主", "pid": 216786, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "谢谢大家！", "timestamp": 1613568592, "type": "text", "url": ""}], "post": {"deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "likenum": 3, "pid": 216786, "reply": 10, "tag": null, "text": "请教dy们，党课的任务量大么？", "timestamp": 1613551308, "type": "text", "updated_at": 1613568590, "url": "", "vote": {}}}